				If you absolutely must have some means of lighting aside from swapping the flashling in an out, try the flare mod.  It modifies the grenades into 10 second flares which you can toss into dark corners and such.  Many parts of the game will still be less engrossing, but it's better than the duct tape mod.
<br />

